Detailed Description

Reply to a CheckUserPasswordRequestPacket.

If the password and logon in the request was correct the UIN of the user is returned in this packet.

{tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ USER_REPLY_HEADER_SIZE & 4 bytes & UIN \ +4 & 2 bytes & sessionID strlen \ +6 & 2 bytes & sessionKey strlen \ & string & sessionID \ & string & sessionKey \ {tabular}
